## A small question, for you only

It's been about half an hour. You went from blank page to a live URL someone else can open.

If the answer surprised you — if you felt the thing the people who use Claude Code keep talking about — there's one quiet test of whether this was the moment or just a moment: **did you text a friend within 24 hours about what you just built?**

You don't need to send the answer anywhere. Nobody's tracking it. But if you didn't, ask yourself why. And if you did, notice that the thing you texted them about was probably not the code.

